Package: usfootballR
Title: Functions to Access MLS and NWSL Play by Play Data
Version: 1.2.1
Authors@R: c(person('Saiem', 'Gilani', email = 'saiem.gilani@gmail.com',role = c('aut','cre')))
Description: A utility for working with American soccer data. A scraping and aggregating interface for ESPN's<https://www.espn.com> MLS and NWSL statistics. It provides users with the capability to access the ESPN API's game play-by-plays, box scores, standings and results to analyze the data for themselves.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
